<div class='container'>
    <div class='row'>
      <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-10 col-sm-12 mx-6 mx-sm-auto px-auto my-5">
        <div class="home-box row d-flex justify-content-center mb-5">
          <%= image_tag 'forest.jpg', class:"w-75 home-image" %>
          <%= image_tag 'hitotabi-home.png', class:"home-logo" %>
          <div class="home-text-area">
            <p class="home-text mt-5"><span>あなたもひと旅いかがですか?</span></p>
            <p class="home-text"><span>土地の風景などを投稿し、</span></p>
            <p class="home-text"><span>穏やかにその雰囲気を味わうこととができるSNSです。</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="content-wrap">
          <header class="page-header heading">
            <h1 class="mb-5 heading__ttl">
              <span class="text-en">home</span>
              <span class="text-ja">ページ</span>
            </h1>
          </header>
        </div>
        <div class="archive-nav">
          <ul class="page-list">
            <li class="is-current"><%= link_to "すべて", posts_path, class:"link" %></li>
            <% if user_signed_in? %>
              <li><%= link_to "行ってみたい場所", favorites_users_path(@user), class:"link" %></li>
              <li><%= link_to "おすすめ", recommend_users_path(@user), class:"link" %></li>
            <% end %>
            <li><%= link_to "タグから探す", tags_path, class:"link" %></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="row" id="bottom">
          <div class='col-md-12 mb-5'>
            <div class="d-flex align-content-start row flex-wrap py-1">
              <%= render '/public/posts/index', posts: @posts %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>